# Healthcare Project Structure & Organization Guidelines

## Root Directory Healthcare Organization

- [app/](mdc:app/): Next.js App Router with healthcare domain routing (dashboard, appointments, auth)
- [components/](mdc:components/): Healthcare-specific React components organized by domain
- [lib/](mdc:lib/): Healthcare utilities, configurations, and shared business logic
- [services/](mdc:services/): Healthcare API services and business logic layer
- [types/](mdc:types/): TypeScript healthcare domain type definitions
- [store/](mdc:store/): Healthcare state management (appointments, patient data)
- [hooks/](mdc:hooks/): Custom React hooks for healthcare functionality
- [utils/](mdc:utils/): Healthcare-specific utility functions and helpers
- [auth/](mdc:auth/): Authentication and authorization configurations
- [providers/](mdc:providers/): React context providers for healthcare data
- [templates/email/](mdc:templates/email/): Healthcare email template system
- [functions/client/](mdc:functions/client/): Client-side healthcare business functions

## Healthcare App Directory Structure

- **Public Routes**: `app/(public)/` for non-authenticated healthcare information
- **Authentication**: `app/auth/` with `login/`, `register/`, `forgot-password/` subdirectories
- **Patient Portal**: `app/appointments/` with create, manage, and proceed workflows
- **Provider Dashboard**: `app/dashboard/` with healthcare provider tools:
  - `appointments/` - Appointment management for providers
  - `doctors/` - Healthcare provider management
  - `patients/` - Patient management and records
  - `services/` - Medical service management
  - `drugs/` - Medication and pharmacy management
  - `users/` - System user management
  - `organizations/` - Multi-tenant organization management
  - `emails/` - Healthcare communication management
  - `newsletters/` - Patient communication and outreach
- **Profile Management**: `app/profile/` for user profile and preferences
- **Subdomain Support**: `app/s/[subdomain]/` for multi-tenant healthcare organizations

