## Healthcare API & Services Architecture

- **API Routes**: `app/api/v1/` with healthcare domain organization (future implementation)
- **Service Layer**: `services/` organized by healthcare domains:
  - `services/client/` - Client-side service functions:
    - `appointment/` - Appointment management services
    - `doctor/` - Healthcare provider services
    - `patient/` - Patient management services
    - `drug/` - Medication management services
    - `email/` - Healthcare communication services
    - `newsletters/` - Patient outreach services
    - `service/` - Medical service management
  - `services/common/` - Shared healthcare services:
